{"title_page": "University of Western Macedonia", "text_new": "{{Infobox university\n|name            = University of Western Macedonia\n|native_name     = \u03a0\u03b1\u03bd\u03b5\u03c0\u03b9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae\u03bc\u03b9\u03bf \u0394\u03c5\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae\u03c2 \u039c\u03b1\u03ba\u03b5\u03b4\u03bf\u03bd\u03af\u03b1\u03c2\n|established     = 2004\n|image_name      = University of Western Macedonia logo.gif\n|image_size      = 200px\n|city            = [[Kozani]], [[Florina]] ([[Western Macedonia]])\n|country         = [[Greece]]\n|type = [[public university|Public]]<br />[[List of universities in Greece|Greece University System]]<br />[[Higher education|Higher Education Institution]]\n|website         = [http://uowm.gr/en/ uowm.gr]\n|}}\n\nThe '''University of Western Macedonia''' ('''UoWM'''; Greek: \u03a0\u03b1\u03bd\u03b5\u03c0\u03b9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae\u03bc\u03b9\u03bf \u0394\u03c5\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae\u03c2 \u039c\u03b1\u03ba\u03b5\u03b4\u03bf\u03bd\u03af\u03b1\u03c2) is a multi-campus university in [[Western Macedonia]] region of Greece.<ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM Report 2014\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/idruma_2009-2013.pdf |title=Internal Evaluation Report, 2014 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref><ref name=\"MODIP Reports\u2013 UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/index.php/tm-eval-reports/tm-int-eval |title=UoWM Evaluation Reports |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language= |accessdate=}}</ref> It was established on 2004 by four departments that had previously formed part of the [[Aristotle University of Thessaloniki]].<ref name=\"History - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://uowm.gr/en/the-university/history/ |title=History - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=University of Western Macedonia |accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==Faculties and departments==\nThe University today consists of three Schools and six Departments, offering undergraduate and postgraduate study programmes.<ref name=\"Faculties - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://uowm.gr/en/education-en/faculties-and-departments/ |title=Faculties - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=uowm.gr |accessdate=}}</ref><ref name=\"Postgraduate studies - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://uowm.gr/en/education-en/postgraduate-studies/ |title=Postgraduate studies - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=uowm.gr |accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Schools\n! Departments\n|-\n! School of Engineering\n([[Kozani]])\n|\n* Department of [[Mechanical Engineering]] <ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM \u039cechEng Report 2015\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/mech/ese_tmm_2014_2015.pdf |title=Department of Mechanical Engineering, Internal Evaluation Report, 2015 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref>\n* Department of [[Computer engineering|Informatics and Telecommunications Engineering]] <ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM ICTE Report 2015\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/icte/ese_tmpt_2014_2015.pdf |title=Department of Informatics and Telecommunications Engineering, Internal Evaluation Report, 2015 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref>\n* Department of Environmental Engineering <ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM EnvEng Report 2015\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/envg/odigos_spoudwn_envg_2015-2016_en.pdf |title=Department of Environmental Engineering, Study Guide, 2015 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language= |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n! School of Education\n([[Florina]])\n|\n* Department of [[Primary education|Primary Education]] <ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM PrimaryEd Report 2015\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/eled/ese_ptde_2014_15.pdf |title=Department of Primary Education, Internal Evaluation Report, 2015 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref>\n* Department of [[Preschool|Early Childhood Education]] <ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM Preschool Report 2015\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/nured/ese_ptn_2014_2015.pdf |title=Department of Early Childhood Education, Internal Evaluation Report, 2015 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n! School of Fine Arts\n([[Florina]])\n|\n* Department of Fine and Applied [[The arts|Arts]] <ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM Applied Arts Report 2015\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/eetf/ese_eetf_2014_2015.pdf |title=Department of Fine and Applied Arts, Internal Evaluation Report, 2015 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n</center>\n\n==Research==\nResearch is conducted by graduate students and members of the faculty, as well as associated researchers.<ref name=\"Research Committee - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://rc.uowm.gr/?lang=en |title=Research Committee - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=rc.uowm.gr |accessdate=}}</ref><ref name=\"Research Committee 2010-2014 - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://rc.uowm.gr/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/ELKE-Apologismos_10-14.pdf |title=UoWM Research Committee Report 2010-2014 |language=el |publisher=rc.uowm.gr |accessdate=}}</ref>\n\nIn April 2018, the students from the [[Hyperion Robotics]] team at the University of Western Macedonia presented an automated system with [[Artificial intelligence|AI]] algorithms called \"Cronus\" claimed to be unbeatable at chess. The project took four months, the idea came from the Dean of the Polytechnic School, Professor Theodoros Theodoulides who is a chess player.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://greece.greekreporter.com/2018/04/28/greek-students-create-unbeatable-chess-robot/|title=Greek Students Create 'Unbeatable' Chess Robot {{!}} GreekReporter.com|last=Kokkinidis|first=Tasos|language=en-US|access-date=2019-03-29}}</ref>\n\nIn March 2019, it was announced that the University of Western Macedonia, among 18 research institutes and companies from seven countries ([[Denmark]], [[Greece]], [[Spain]], [[Norway]], [[Poland]], [[Portugal]], and [[Switzerland]]), takes part in the project of [[European Commission]]'s [[Horizon 2020]] programme for research and training in 5G mobile networks, named TeamUp5G.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://eurekalert.org/multimedia_ml/pub/7696.php|title=The UC3M is coordinating a European project for research and training in 5G mobile networks|website=EurekAlert|language=en|access-date=2019-03-29}}</ref> Coordinated by [[Charles III University of Madrid|UC3M]], the project is being carried out, within the framework of the [[Marie Curie|Marie Sklodowska-Curie]] Innovative Training Networks, between the year 2019 and 2022.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dicyt.com/viewNews.php?newsId=40350|title=Iniciativa internacional para investigar y formar en redes m\u00f3viles 5G|website=www.dicyt.com|language=es|access-date=2019-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.it.pt/Projects/Index/4556|title=New RAN TEchniques for 5G UltrA-dense Mobile networks TeamUp5G|website=www.it.pt|access-date=2019-03-29}}</ref>\n\n==Academic evaluation==\nIn 2016 the external evaluation committee gave University of Western Macedonia a ''Positive evaluation''.<ref name=\"HQAA External Evaluation Reports of Institutions\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.adip.gr/instevalreports/FINAL%20EXTERNAL%20EVALUATION%20REPORT_UNIVERSITY%20OF%20WESTERN%20MACEDONIA.pdf |title=University of Western Macedonia - External Evaluation Report |language=en |date=2016 |publisher=www.adip.gr}}\"''The EEC has decided to give to UoWM a positive evaluation. UoWM has self-motivated, dynamic and recognized faculty. Several research units at UoWM are productive, visible, and deliver good quality research. The size, dispersion, and diversity of the Institution need to be thoroughly addressed, since they  may produce serious obstacles to the viability of the Institution.''\"</ref>\n\nAn external evaluation of all academic departments in [[List of universities in Greece|Greek universities]] was conducted by the Hellenic Quality Assurance and Accreditation Agency (HQA).<ref name=\"UoWM - External Evaluation Reports of Departments\">External Evaluation Reports of Departments 2013-2014 by the HQA.\n* [http://www.adip.gr/external/UniWestMaced_MechEng_2013.pdf Department of Mechanical Engineering (2013)]\n* [http://www.adip.gr/external/UniWestMaced_InfoComEng_2013.pdf Department of Informatics and Telecommunications Engineering (2013)] \n* [http://www.adip.gr/external/UniWestMaced_EarlyChildhoodEdu_2013.pdf Department of Early Childhood Education (2013)] \n* [http://www.adip.gr/external/UniWestMaced_AppliedArts_2014.pdf Department of Fine and Applied Arts (2014)] {{in lang|el}}\n* [http://www.adip.gr/external/UniWestMaced_PrimaryEdu_2014.pdf Department of Primary Education (2014)]\n</ref>\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of universities in Greece]]\n* [[List of research institutes in Greece]]\n* [[Aristotle University of Thessaloniki]], the largest university in the [[Balkans]], established in 1925.\n* [[University of Ioannina]], a university established in the city of [[Ioannina]], established in 1970.\n* [[TEI of Western Macedonia|Technological Educational Institute of Western Macedonia]]\n* [[Education in Greece]]\n* [[Academic grading in Greece]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n{{Greek Universities}}\n\n{{coord|40.3027|N|21.7931|E|source:wikidata|display=title}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Western Macedonia, University of}}\n[[Category:Universities in Greece]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 2002]]\n[[Category:Kozani]]\n[[Category:Education in Western Macedonia]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Western Macedonia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox University\n|name            = University of Western Macedonia\n|native_name     = \u03a0\u03b1\u03bd\u03b5\u03c0\u03b9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae\u03bc\u03b9\u03bf \u0394\u03c5\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae\u03c2 \u039c\u03b1\u03ba\u03b5\u03b4\u03bf\u03bd\u03af\u03b1\u03c2\n|established     = 2004\n|image_name      = University of Western Macedonia logo.gif\n|image_size      = 200px\n|city            = [[Kozani]], [[Florina]] ([[Western Macedonia]])\n|country         = [[Greece]]\n|type = [[public university|Public]]<br />[[List of universities in Greece|Greece University System]]<br />[[Higher education|Higher Education Institution]]\n|website         = [http://uowm.gr/en/ uowm.gr]\n|}}\n\nThe '''University of Western Macedonia''' ('''UoWM'''; Greek: \u03a0\u03b1\u03bd\u03b5\u03c0\u03b9\u03c3\u03c4\u03ae\u03bc\u03b9\u03bf \u0394\u03c5\u03c4\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae\u03c2 \u039c\u03b1\u03ba\u03b5\u03b4\u03bf\u03bd\u03af\u03b1\u03c2) is a multi-campus university in [[Western Macedonia]] region of Greece.<ref name=\"MODIP \u2013 UoWM Report 2014\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/images/pdf/idruma_2009-2013.pdf |title=Internal Evaluation Report, 2014 |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language=el |accessdate=}}</ref><ref name=\"MODIP Reports\u2013 UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://modip.uowm.gr/fe/index.php/tm-eval-reports/tm-int-eval |title=UoWM Evaluation Reports |publisher=modip.uowm.gr |language= |accessdate=}}</ref> It was established on 2004 by four departments that had previously formed part of the [[Aristotle University of Thessaloniki]].<ref name=\"History - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://uowm.gr/en/the-university/history/ |title=History - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=University of Western Macedonia |accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n==Faculties and departments==\nThe University today consists of three Schools and six Departments, offering undergraduate and postgraduate study programmes.<ref name=\"Faculties - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://uowm.gr/en/education-en/faculties-and-departments/ |title=Faculties - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=uowm.gr |accessdate=}}</ref><ref name=\"Postgraduate studies - UoWM\">{{cite web|url=https://uowm.gr/en/education-en/postgraduate-studies/ |title=Postgraduate studies - University of Western Macedonia |publisher=uowm.gr |accessdate=}}</ref>\n\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n