{"title_page": "University of West Kordofan", "text_new": "{{Infobox university\n|name            = University of Western Kordofan\n|native_name     = <big>\u062c\u0627\u0645\u0639\u0629 \u063a\u0631\u0628 \u0643\u0631\u062f\u0641\u0627\u0646</big>\n|image           = \n|established     = \n|type            = Public<ref>{{cite web\n |url=http://www.mohe.gov.sd/\n |publisher   = Ministry of Higher Education & Scientific Research\n |title=Sudanese higher education\n |accessdate=2011-09-15}}</ref>\n|vice-president  = \n|city            = [[Al-Foula]]\n|country         = [[Sudan]]\n|state           = [[South Kordofan]]\n|undergrad       =\n|postgrad        =\n|master          =\n|phd             =\n|staff           =\n|website         ={{url|http://www.uwkordofan.net/}}\n}}\nThe '''University of Western Kordofan''' (or Jameat Gareb Kordofan) is a university in the state of [[Western Kordofan]], [[Sudan]]. It is based in [[Al-Foula]], but has campuses in [[Khartoum]], [[Babanusa]], [[Balnhod]] and [[Abozbd]].<ref>{{cite web\n |url=http://www.uwkordofan.net/\n |title=University of Western Kordofan\n |publisher=University of Western Kordofan\n |accessdate=2011-09-15}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n{{coord missing|Sudan}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:West Kordofan, University of}}\n[[Category:Universities and colleges in Sudan]]\n[[Category:South Kordofan]]\n[[Category:Educational institutions established in 1990]]\n\n\n{{Sudan-university-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox_University\n|name            = University of Western Kordofan\n|native_name     = <big>\u062c\u0627\u0645\u0639\u0629 \u063a\u0631\u0628 \u0643\u0631\u062f\u0641\u0627\u0646</big>\n|image           = \n|established     = \n|type            = Public<ref>{{cite web\n |url=http://www.mohe.gov.sd/\n |publisher   = Ministry of Higher Education & Scientific Research\n |title=Sudanese higher education\n |accessdate=2011-09-15}}</ref>\n|vice-president  = \n|city            = [[Al-Foula]]\n|c